Whoever has the loudest
press release, I guess.

00:47:02.240 --> 00:47:05.070
&gt;&gt; And then my final
question was,

00:47:05.070 --> 00:47:09.710
I was curious how far we
were behind those countries.

00:47:09.710 --> 00:47:11.010
If you could kind
of give examples --

00:47:11.010 --> 00:47:14.690
you spoke a little bit about
it in the answer earlier

00:47:14.690 --> 00:47:17.680
about Germany, but
I was just curious

00:47:17.680 --> 00:47:21.660
