You can kind of see
some of the same thing

00:55:16.810 --> 00:55:21.010
in the OSRD organization in that
they did it all by contract,

00:55:21.010 --> 00:55:23.280
and they contracted
out to research centers

00:55:23.280 --> 00:55:25.170
at universities --
some in industry,

00:55:25.170 --> 00:55:26.750
but mostly at universities --

00:55:26.750 --> 00:55:30.240
and if they needed
a temporary sort

00:55:30.240 --> 00:55:32.540
of research center,
it would be built.

00:55:32.540 --> 00:55:35.500
And then they would staff it
from the university staffs.

00:55:35.500 --> 00:55:39.930
And so that was kind
of the same model.

00:55:39.930 --> 00:55:42.080
And then, but after the war,

00:55:42.080 --> 00:55:43.600
most of those research
centers went away,

00:55:43.600 --> 00:55:45.860
and they were replaced, as
you saw, over the years,

00:55:45.860 --> 00:55:49.860
with other research centers
dedicated to other purposes.

00:55:51.150 --> 00:55:53.510
Thank you very much.

